Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight Gaki is going to a town they have never been to and asking them the best 5 places: Part 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They will draw one of the lots with the names of all the stations in the Kanto region and find out the best 5 places recommended by locals in towns they have never been to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the station that Housei drew?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Iwai?\N- Iwai??
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's JR Iwai Station in Minami-Boso City, Chiba Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the top 5 recommended by its locals?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, what is the 5th place recommended by Kawana-san, who has lived in Iwai for 30 years, whom we met in front of the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Iwai Beach, which is popular among locals and sightseers alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, but there are some people.\N- There are some people!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The view is very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:00:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they interviewed people who were at Iwai Beach for the 4th place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuura-san, who has been visiting this beach for 30 years, told them about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.93,0:01:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, there is a observatory on Mt. Tomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Observatory on Mt. Tomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go there on foot, won't we die?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They headed to the observatory of Mt. Tomi, which is said to have beautiful views, and they climbed the mountain in temperatures over 30°C (86°F).
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is intense hiking!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is intense hiking in the middle of summer.\NAnd I'm wearing Crocs!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then 35 minutes had passed since they started their climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes 45 minutes from here to the observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:01:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll split up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If we all climb up, we will run out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One of us should climb it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They decided to play rock-paper-scissors and only the loser would climb the mountain.\N- First comes rock, rock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would climb among Matsumoto, Housei and Endo?\N- First comes rock, rock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay, I'll go.\N- Shozo Endo will go climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo has to go alone to the observatory of Mt. Tomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Top 5 recommended places around Iwai station.\NWhat on earth will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Subbed by RAIDEN1017]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo set off alone for the observatory at Mt. Tomi, the 4th recommended place to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, this is too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really afraid of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's pretty dangerous here.\N- Really so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I lose because I sang Miss Brand-New Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo climbs up the mountain trail\Nin temperatures over 30 ℃.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!!\NThis is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is insane.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for Endo, the four of them came to Iwai Station again to ask the locals for the 3rd recommended place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,First, Housei and Tanaka went to the tourist information center at the station to ask around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did you get any good information?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- First, they introduced us to that mountain associated with Satomi Hakkenden.\N- Yeah, we went the mountain earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- And the sea.\N- Yeah, we went there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hi!\NYou're  the owner of the gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to mention this, have you guys been to Furari?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a road station named Furari
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They were talked by Kawana-san, the man with the shiny gold teeth, who told them about the 5th place, Iwai Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They asked Kawana-san for his 3rd recommended place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a roadside station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The roadside station?\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What did they introduce you guys to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's the  roadside station too.\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to go with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want him to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think he's a replacement for Endo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll go to the roadside station.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything we don't understand, we'll come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come out when I clap my hands like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a pond fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They immediately headed for the roadside station he had told them about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Endo had been climbing the mountain alone for 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Too hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea that today's shoot would be this tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, Endo continued to climb the steep mountain trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really tough.\NWhat are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This would be impossible for Downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And Matsumoto-san was wearing Crocs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He would never have expected this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lose weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you ready to head to the observatory?\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't go to the observatory I would be really pissed off at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the four of them were driving to the roadside station recommended as the 3rd recommendedd place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Endo eat anything in the waiting room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, he didn't eat anything.\N- He must be starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't eat anything on the move either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The roadside station is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's big.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't all locals come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They arrived at the recommended roadside station, Furari, and immediately went inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Biwa-chan, the Chiba-only mascot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she a biwa(loquat) ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't this be 2nd place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone says so, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the roadside station only on the first floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There is also the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is on the second floor?\N- There is a restaurant and a food court on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can I eat local food on the second floor?\N- Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, they have a restaurant here on the second floor where you can eat local food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any recommendations?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- How about sangayaki?\N- Sangayaki! Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's that?\N- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go there and check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They decided to eat the famous sangayaki on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I eat what I bought here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a food court.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They sell ramen and many other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It says "sangayaki" here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's sangayaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it's minced horse mackerel with green onion, miso and ginger.\NEating it raw is Namerou, and grilled one is called Sanga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whale and sanga are recommended.\NYou can try them if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give me four sangayaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to try the meat-wrapped sausage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:09:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of them each chose what they wanted to eat and bought six items, including sangayaki and whale mince cutlets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like tsumire(fish meatball).
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This one tastes like sardine tsumire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, Endo had been climbing the mountain alone for 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mt. Tomi Love Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"We set up the love bell on this Mt. Tomi so that the sound of love would echo through the climbers."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ring this bell for everyone at the bottom of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,May love come to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- For everyone.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Endo is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy hasn't eaten anything, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we buy Endo something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we sure we don't need to buy him anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's going to the observatory instead of all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because he lost at rock-paper-scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Roadside Station, Furari Tomiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The first floor sells flesh local fish and vegetables landed at the local fishing port.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,On the second floor, you can enjoy gourmet foods such as sangayaki made with horse mackerel from Minami-Boso.\NThis place is popular among tourists and locals alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the 3rd recommended place around Iwai Station was recognized as the Roadside Station, Furari Tomiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:11:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then 45 minutes passed since Endo started climbing the mountain alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the place!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look, look!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a spectacular view!\NIt's really a spectacular view.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fantastic!\NYou can see the whole Iwai from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good enough to be the 1st place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it should be the 1st place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mt. Tomi was the setting for the chuanqi novel Nanso Satomi Hakkenden, and is also a popular hiking course with views of Tokyo Bay and the Miura Peninsula.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mt. Tomi was recognized as the 4th recommended place around Iwai Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This spectacular view that I saw after all this hard work is the 1st place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the 4th place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this in the 4th place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They found the 5th to 3rd recommended places.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they asked the clerks for the 2nd place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your 2nd recommended place around Iwai station?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- I've only lived here a short time.\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mountain...? Hmmm..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any shops?\NWhere is the place that sells your favorite food?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Loquat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who answered "loquat" was Aoki-san, who has lived in Iwai for more than 70 years.\NWhat's her 2nd recommendation for this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- A shop selling sweets made from loquat is located along Iwai Beach.\N- Sound's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the name of the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Takayama Confectionery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Takayama Confectionery?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard there is a famous loquat sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The old lady at the store there told me about the famous loquat sweets at a shop called Takayama Confectionery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We should go there.\NThis town is famous for loquat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- So, shall we go to the place that sells the famous loquat sweets?\N- Yes! Let's go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They headed to Takayama Confectionery for the loquat sweets she told them about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is a nice town, isn't it?\N- Yes, it's a peaceful town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Tanaka from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Toyonaka City in Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else does come from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi Fujii is also from that neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- There are many comedians who are from that area.\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:14:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- What about Hyogo?\N- Surprisingly, there are not that many. Not even in Amagasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are a lot of actresses from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where are they from?\N- Hyogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Many actresses are from Hyogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiko Kitagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki Aibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoko Minamino.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is the same true of Yoko Minamino?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mako Ishino.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoko Ishino.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They are taking the world by storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And the car arrived near Takayama Confectionery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was called Sunada, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Sunada?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The loquat sweets shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The shop is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No one said anything about the Sunada!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It says "Sunada Guest House".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Here we are!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- What was the name of the shop again?\N- Takayama Confectionery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a tasteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It says "loquat buns".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka, you go run to the shop and ask for permission to shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- You are asking me to help, right?\N- Are you going to make us wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You are asking me to help, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You really surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They asked the shopkeeper for permission to shoot and went inside the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of sweets do you recommend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this loquat bun a specialty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a mixture of loquat and white bean paste in this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that the specialty of this shop?\N- Yes, it's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is this what that old lady was talking about?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We will buy this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How long has this shop been in business?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's been in business since my father and grandfather, since the Taisho era.\N- Taisho era!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They were asking the third generation owner about the store.\NThen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shocked you could made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you guys were very lucky to win that rock-paper-scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- My knees are still shaking.\N- Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The slope from...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The slope from there was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just talking to Mister, so I don't need to talk about it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about your story!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the wrong place at the wrong time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for the mister he was just talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They ate the shop's recommendation of loquat buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- You were craving sugar, right?\N- That's really true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Really so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a slightly sour taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This loquat bun is a famous confectionery representing Minami-Boso, made from loquat produced in Minami-Boso, jammed with just enough loquat grains to remain, and baked with white bean paste and kneaded loquat paste in a sponge cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the 2nd recommendation around Iwai Station is recognized as Loquat Manju of Takayama Confectionery !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They asked the clerk for the 1st recommended place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anywhere around here you recommend we should go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What places do you recommend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the 1st recommended place for Shingo Takayama, the 4th generation owner of Takayama Confectionery, who was born and raised in Iwai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunset is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Beautiful sunset?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we watch it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if the 1st place is the sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto was worried.\NThen ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwai beach is also good, but there is a famous pier on Haraoka beach, about 10 minutes away by car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a popular spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the 1st place is the pier?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a wooden pier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- But let's go back to the front of the station and ask God, too.\N- No,no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is God?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean the Golden God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's go to the pier.\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They were headed for Haraoka Beach, where there was a wooden pier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, we can go to the 1st recommended place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a lot has happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo, do you know why you lost rock-paper-scissors?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to think about it, but I couldn't figure it out either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo, you are an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After we said, "first comes rock," we all definitely thought you would make a move other than rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I played scissors both times and lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm confident that I can play rock-paper-scissors with Endo and not lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I might lose to you the first turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But from the next turn, I can read your moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,From the second turn, I'm confident that I can beat you five times in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay, let's play.\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.99,0:19:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't count the first turn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,First comes rock, rock-paper-scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- See, I told you.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,First comes rock, rock-paper-scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I explained it the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You explained it the other way around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- I won.\N- Because I explained it the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to tell you that I was definitely going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My explanation was the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.\NThe exact opposite of the explanation you gave happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He played the same move twice in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And he lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what I said was not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with this.\NMy explanation was the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's necessary to explain it the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,On the one hand, there is that way of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a different atmosphere from that beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the pier?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:21:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that the pier?\N- That's good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the pier?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be nice to walk there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They parked their car near the first recommended pier and walked to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- It was cooler.\N- It's just the perfect temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like simeppoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Simeppoi(Gloomy) ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is "simeppoi," which means appropriate for the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That "Simeppoi" will definitely come across wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally they came to the pier, the 1st recommended place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.04,0:21:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- And it says you can see Mt. Fuji from here.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimi-no-oka.\N(A hill with a view of Mt. Fuji.)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:21:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The picture is on the back of the sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you can see Mt. Fuji from the front here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't see it at all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But aren't we awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's great, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.43,0:22:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't you think it's great?\N- I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got a retro vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.77,0:22:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's made of wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm glad she told me about this.\N- Really so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This deserves 1st place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to walk on the pier.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okamoto Pier is one of the few wooden piers in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.54,0:23:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a popular spot to watch the sunset with a spectacular view.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.18,0:23:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And when the sun goes down, the bare bulbs on the pier light up and you can enjoy the retro vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okamoto Pier on Haraoka Beach was recognized as the 1st recommended place around Iwai Station!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This was tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.64,0:23:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My knees are still shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.90,0:23:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mt. Tomi was recommended by many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone recommended this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't get to see that view.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch it on the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.05,0:23:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's broadcast that footage in picture-in-picture.\N- What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.58,0:23:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked hard though...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.99,0:23:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Subbed by RAIDEN1017]
